data.description: Renovated & improved in 2013, this 3 bed 3 bath home with a glorious front porch beckons you to sit a while. Hurry to see this beautiful home located in one of the most sought after neighborhoods in San Marco. 2nd level has Owner's Suite with 2 large walk in closets & owners bath, 2 add'l bedrooms & shared bath. 1st level has Main living room, family room with atrium doors & additional flex space near laundry & full bath. Convenient for in & outside use you'll find the beautifully appointed wet bar with cabinetry overlooking backyard & porches. Viking gas stove, farm sink & wine cooler add to chefs kitchen. Perfectly located at the end of a quaint street for privacy. 2 car detached garage & room for a pool. Roof 9yrs, Porch Roof 4yrs, HVAC 9 yrs, Washer & Dryer included.
